name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Victoria Real Estate Statement of Information

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Showing Victoria real estate statement of information on domain.com.au and realestate.com.au websites

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Real estate listings in Victoria, Australia require to have a statement of information showing the indicative price range of the property.

This extension help save time on the top 2 property websites domain.com.au and realestate.com.au by displaying a Statement of Information button on the top, and showing the document in an overlay on the same page. This means no more wasting time searching for the document and navigating between the document tab and the listing tab.

Please be advised this extension is intended for entertainment purposes only. The information provided by this extension should not be used for making financial or investment decisions, or any general decisions. The creator of this extension accepts no liability for any errors or omissions in the information provided. Use of this extension is at your own risk.
